                        <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/4417: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-06-06T15:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">June 6,
                                        1922—3 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>141. Your 245 June 3, 7 P.M.</p>
                        <p>Your telegrams of May 26 and June 3, 2 P.M. to Mukden are approved.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
